night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037814961968080772"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1b2oko3N36ZiEAMaCTExOTQ4NjI1OCDzkY/QBjAAOE1AEXITMjAzNzgxNDk2MTk2ODA4MDc3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1778682889.305054", "card_id": "Q_1920476766822196853", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "古希腊雕塑非常精美，但是为什么都是坦胸露乳，不穿衣服？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "相对应我国的塑像，人偶，各种佣一般身上都会有相应的时期、阶层的服装，尤其是各种宗教场所的神像更是衣着华贵。而反观古希腊雕塑，不管是不是神明、平民，大多数雕刻精美的确都是不着片缕坦胸露乳，这是为什么？为何两边反差如此之大？还是没有羞耻观念？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e2817efd92adbe6a9322eba6dd2887a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1920476766822196853"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1b2oko3N36ZiEAMaCTExNTUxMzQ4MCC90uPCBjAAOHZAEnITMTkyMDQ3Njc2NjgyMjE5Njg1M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1778682889.305464", "card_id": "Q_2037605624997831504", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "历史爱好者们，你们在历史猜猜看（When & Where）的这个 AI 猜图小游戏里能拿多少分？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "游戏地址：wen-ware.com 我觉得自己还可以，目前最高分：历史学家。 目前能快速猜对历史事件（基本上就能锁定出地点），但忘了精确时间 猜不出来的就推理，然后随手标一个点（大概率是时间对了地点错误） 各位历史老爷们，来看看实力？（笑 不过遇到这种邪乎的场景就崩溃了： 还有一些送分题："}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e57a3824f9019d272ced0a55545fb7f5_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037605624997831504"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1b2oko3N36ZiEAMaCTExOTQ4MTI2OCD9i4zQBjAAOFhAE3ITMjAzNzYwNTYyNDk5NzgzMTUwNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1778682889.306511", "card_id": "Q_2036474157798352419", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "吕严和母亲上节目之后联系更频繁了，也解开了「空箱子」误会，有些亲子问题的本质是不是因为缺乏沟通？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 7 日，吕严发布视频分享母亲来京探望自己的日常。在车内聊天时，两人聊起此前节目中提及的「母子矛盾」——关于小时候母亲是否给自己买电脑一事。原来，当年母亲已经买下电脑，只是担心之后会降价，恰逢有人想买，便暂时转手卖出。而吕严当时并未询问缘由，只是默默记在心里。后来因为吕严成绩未达标，母亲便没有再重新购买电脑，这才导致他一直误以为母亲当初根本没买。如今两人就此事解开多年心结。 现实中没有综艺搭桥牵线，你觉得成年子女和父母，应该如何打破这种几十年形成的隔阂与心理壁垒？你的成长过程中，有没有这样一个空箱子？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-96e4dc19e3624c6779bccea9b97371e2.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036474157798352419"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1b2oko3N36ZiEAMaCTExOTQ0MTYwMyC70PvPBjAAOBtAFHITMjAzNjQ3NDE1Nzc5ODM1MjQxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1778682889.307248", "card_id": "Q_2037693128816185900", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你觉得松下 LUMIX 新机 L10 怎么样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-00532a5818c65a48014504698428940f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2037693128816185900"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI1b2oko3N36ZiEAMaCTExOTQ4NDU1MSD8ro3QBjAAOD5AFXITMjAzNzY5MzEyODgxNjE4NTkwMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1778682889.307565", "card_id": "Q_572947718", "f